   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Build homes for families living in extreme poverty</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">With your help we will build Diana Rosa and 9 Peruvian families living in extreme poverty a descent home. They currently live in houses which walls and roof are made from reed mats and plastic bags. Due to the weather conditions and a lack of proper medical care, a high percentage of this families children suffer from deceases such as bronchitis and bone aches because they don&apos;t have the proper protection from the cold weather. Help us build them a House of Wood. Help us save their lives.</narrative>
  </description>
